Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作品是設想在首都東京地區發生巨大地震災害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在充分調查與查證的基礎上所製作的虛構故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作力求體現真實性 通過模擬實驗而著成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也存在與現實事物描寫方式不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天儘是些令人討厭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界乾脆毀滅掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:56.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}「 世 界 、 崩 潰 」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 你要堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕點 輕點 注意點很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻愣著站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你有沒有見到一個小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定還在廁所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口在前方 請別慌張緩步慢行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我回來 那邊很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的小女孩 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊不可以過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才發生地震時那邊起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可謂是千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才遇見的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一個人嗎 剛才和你在一起的弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他一個人去上廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你爸媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和弟弟兩個人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我讓他一個人去廁所的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟的名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去找你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次地震很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你有沒有看到小男孩 七八歲模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子是有看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過都是和父母在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請問你有沒有看到小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概這麼高 七八歲模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著帶著黃色的綠色T恤  胸部這裡有一條橫線的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在一樓玩具店看到有幾個男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找其他的樓梯 這邊很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小姐姐 拜託你了 別胡來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該知道那很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是悠貴還在玩具店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果連你也受傷 那就失去了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼連我也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是還不知道悠貴現在有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是我說的不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟肯定沒事 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會陪你一起找的 所以你不要再亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點點 好 一二用力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 大家有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這邊已經很危險了 你們也快點去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在找小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著帶著黃色的綠色T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經粗略地找過一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們最後發現的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的孩子可能已經
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 你在哪裡 快回答 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我們暫且出去 這邊很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著煙霧還未佈滿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 如果要走的話 請你一個人出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能拋棄悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你想想 怎樣才能夠活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴也是 如果活著肯定在避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著才能找到悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便你買點飲料回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲料 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨這個地方 請讓我去找下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 在這裡 請救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 是姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我馬上救你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶著那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 你沒事太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要等雨停嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊很危險 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火災
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的話 就淋不到雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也不行 通信基本被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在報導信息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4小時前 即4點56分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以關東地區為中心發生了大地震
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次地震的震源地為東京灣北部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震源深度約為25公里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示地震規模的震級推測為8.0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8級地震
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請充分注意餘震和海嘯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裡看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機能用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受地震影響發生的交通事故使交通擁堵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據東京消防局提供的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在市內各地發生了規模巨大的火災
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在致力於居民的避難工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在木野田公園附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西條方向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家在三元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 根本就打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有單線能用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們再看一下狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會替你們想回家的辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對我們這麼熱心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 作為一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐很拚命得在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點回去把禮物送給媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 我們還不知道彼此名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是日下部真理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小野澤未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來 真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡姐姐的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起出來玩 關係真融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情會變成這樣也是媽媽的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽總是說工作工作 叫我們兩個人來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好受 我們家是我媽和女兒三人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是因為工作根本顧不上女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的孩子喜歡蕩鞦韆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想著奮力工作 到時搬家到有鞦韆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是迷迷糊糊地 可能她都過了喜歡鞦韆的年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我去拿下行李 摩托車就停在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人可能再也不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 她還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有義務要照顧我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 這是餘震
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發生大地震之後 會出現幾次餘震
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的餘震很小 這邊應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 兩位 肚子有沒有餓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道還是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我孩子的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到今天可就是4歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日下部小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經不成形了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日蛋糕還是圓的好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們暫先休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天肯定會很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磚橋倒塌 多人遇害
